                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18360404-name-1052" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18360404-name-1052" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18360404-name-1052" type="surname" value="BENTLEY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18360404-name-1052" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS BENTLEY</persName>
                  </hi>. I was in the Wheatsheaf-yard, on Islington Green, on Saturday, and saw a person carrying a decanter—he delivered it to the prisoner, who ran off with it—I followed him about one hundred yards, and secured him—I saw a ticket on the decanter, and I had seen it in the prosecutors shop for some time—the person who delivered it to him made his escape—I did not see him take it from the shop—they were about two yards from the prosecutor's shop when it was delivered to the prisoner.</p>
